content.raw:
I get some warnings when running the plane properller demo

~~~
Warning [parser.cc:779] XML Element[use_parent_frame], child of element[axis] not defined in SDF. Ignoring[use_parent_frame]. You may have an incorrect SDF file, or an sdformat version that doesn't support this element.
~~~

should it be `use_parent_model_frame` instead of `use_parent_frame`?
